"In each level, you will be fighting against the AI ​​YOU created in the previous round.\nChoose your blue character to start creating your AI.\nDrag the nodes on the left onto the workspace on the right side,\nClick on the nodes to modify them and connect them to create your AI!\nIf you managed to beat yourself in the previous round,\nDon't worry if you couldn't win!\nUse the newly unlocked nodes to defeat yourself again!\nYou can always modify your AI again and continue the challenge!"